oai_dc:dc.dc:title: pi(4s)+pi(2s) cycloaddition between electron deficient pi-systems and photoreaction of beta,gamma-enones: a novel stereoselective entry into angular triquinanes
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: SINGH, V
LAHIRI, S
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: organic-synthesis
tricyclopentanoids
cyclopropanes
methane
cycloaddition
oxa-di-pi-methane rearrangement
angular triquinane
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Cycloaddition of electron deficient partners such as cyclohexa-2,4-dienone and acrylates leading to an efficient synthesis of complex bicyclo[2.2.2]octenones having a beta,gamma-enone chromophore, and their transformation to angular triquinanes via photoreaction, is described.
